# Linting & Formatting

## Commands
```bash
pnpm lint          # Run ESLint on all apps
pnpm lint:fix      # Auto-fix ESLint issues
pnpm format        # Format with Prettier
pnpm format:check  # Check formatting
```

## Conventions
- ESLint flat config: `apps/backend/eslint.config.js`, `apps/frontend/eslint.config.js`
- Prettier config: `.prettierrc` (singleQuote, trailingComma all, printWidth 100)
- Run `pnpm lint:fix && pnpm format` when blocked by formatting issues
